---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import FAQSection from '@/components/sections/FAQSection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Bill of Lading Converter"
  description="Extract shipper, consignee, carrier, and goods data from bill of lading PDFs automatically. AI-powered OCR with Zapier and n8n integration. Free trial."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.formx.ai/tools/bill-of-lading-converter"
>
  <section class="title-2 bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer pagetitle__container mt-60 w-container">
      <h1 class="pricing-title mb-0">
        <span class="heading-gradient">The Future of Electronic Bill of Lading:&#x2028;<br />&#x200d;</span>Automate Data Extraction Now
      </h1>
      <p class="section__header__content mb-40">Upload your documents and instantly extract data into Excel or CSV. Skip manual entry, boost efficiency, and get ready for the future of electronic bill of lading.</p>
      <div class="w-embed w-iframe">
        <iframe src="https://widgets.formx.ai/bill-of-lading" style="width: 100%; height: 600px" frameBorder="0"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section product-section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper m-reverse">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/pages/converter_privacy.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" />
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">Your Data.Your Privacy.Our Promise.</h2>
          <div class="product-2-block-paragraph">We prioritize user privacy and delete your data after processing with our secure bill of lading OCR.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/pages/converter_bl_features@2x.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            width="600"
            sizes="(max-width: 991px) 100vw, (max-width: 1279px) 45vw, 575.5px"
            alt=""
            srcset="/images/pages/converter_bl_features@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_bl_features@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_bl_features@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_bl_features@2x-p-1600.webp 1600w, /images/pages/converter_bl_features@2x-p-2000.webp 2000w, /images/pages/converter_bl_features@2x.webp 2401w"
            class="image-rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default heading-content w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-wrapper mx-auto mb-60">
        <h2 class="product-heading">What is the Electronic Bill of Lading?</h2>
        <div class="product-subheading">An electronic bill of lading (eBL) is a digital version of the traditional paper-based bill of lading. It serves as a legal document that records the details of a shipment, including the shipper, consignee, carrier, and goods being transported.</div>
      </div>
      <div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="_2-block-flex tabs-with-image w-tabs">
        <div class="hover-change tabs w-tab-menu">
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Digital format</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Eliminates the need for physical documents, reducing paper waste and storage costs.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Real-time access</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Allows authorized parties to view and update shipment information in real time, improving visibility and efficiency.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Enhanced security</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Uses advanced encryption and digital signatures to protect data and prevent fraud.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 4" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Faster processing</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Streamlines the shipping process by reducing manual tasks and paper-based workflows.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 5" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Improved collaboration</div>
            <div class="hover-change-description">Enables better communication and coordination among all parties involved in the shipment.</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="_2-block-flex-image tabs w-tab-content">
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 93vw, (max-width: 767px) 95vw, (max-width: 991px) 46vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, (max-width: 1439px) 595.5px, 575.5px" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_digital-format@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_digital-format@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_digital-format@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_digital-format@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_digital-format@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 93vw, (max-width: 767px) 95vw, (max-width: 991px) 46vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, (max-width: 1439px) 595.5px, 575.5px" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_real-time@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_real-time@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_real-time@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_real-time@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_real-time@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img sizes="(max-width: 479px) 93vw, (max-width: 767px) 95vw, (max-width: 991px) 46vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, (max-width: 1439px) 595.5px, 575.5px" srcset="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_security@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_security@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_security@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_security@2x.webp 1200w" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_security@2x.webp" loading="eager" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 4" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 93vw, (max-width: 767px) 95vw, (max-width: 991px) 46vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, (max-width: 1439px) 595.5px, 575.5px" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_processing@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_processing@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_processing@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_processing@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_processing@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 5" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 93vw, (max-width: 767px) 95vw, (max-width: 991px) 46vw, (max-width: 1279px) 47vw, (max-width: 1439px) 595.5px, 575.5px" alt="" src="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_collaboration@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_collaboration@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_collaboration@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_collaboration@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_bl_whatis_collaboration@2x.webp 1200w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-content-wrapper">
        <div class="product-heading-wrapper">
          <h2 class="product-heading">Break Free from Manual Work:&#x2028;<span class="heading-gradient">Automate Your Document Workflow</span></h2>
          <div class="product-subheading">With Zapier or n8n integration, you can transform time-consuming tasks into automated processes.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-content-wrapper">
          <div class="grid-12 row-gap-60">
            <div id="w-node-_4f1db2a9-0cb0-338e-8ac4-da617c0a309f-208d9a47" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 m-16 bordered first">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">1</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Lack of standardization</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">There is no universally accepted standard for eBL formats, leading to compatibility issues and increased complexity for businesses.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="w-node-_43688fa3-aba8-c30c-31a3-6a8978c29102-208d9a47" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 m-16 bordered first">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">2</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Regulatory hurdles</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">Governments and regulatory bodies may have different requirements for eBLs, making it difficult for businesses to comply with all regulations.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="w-node-_4f1db2a9-0cb0-338e-8ac4-da617c0a30a8-208d9a47" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">3</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Security concerns</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">Ensuring the security of sensitive data transmitted and stored electronically is a major concern, especially in the face of cyber threats.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="w-node-_820c2705-17a8-348f-a37f-c505982d5818-208d9a47" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 m-16 bordered first">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">4</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Infrastructure limitations</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">Some businesses may lack the necessary technology or infrastructure to implement and manage eBLs effectively.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="w-node-_4f1db2a9-0cb0-338e-8ac4-da617c0a30b1-208d9a47" class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white card-content-center p-0 m-16 bordered last">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-center flex-center"><div class="steps-number">5</div></div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text">Resistance to change</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description">There may be resistance from stakeholders who are comfortable with traditional paper-based processes and are hesitant to adopt new technologies.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section product-section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-content-wrapper">
        <div class="product-heading-wrapper mw-80">
          <h2 class="product-heading">The Only Alternative:<br /><span class="heading-gradient">Automate Traditional Bill of Lading with AI</span></h2>
          <div class="product-subheading">While eBL adoption may take time, AI can automate traditional&#x2028;bill of lading processing, improving efficiency and accuracy.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-content-wrapper">
          <div class="_2-block-grid gap-32">
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white p-48">
              <div class="card-svg-block">
                <img src="/images/pages/products_zapier-n8n-integration-automation-whyformx-ai.svg" loading="lazy" width="128" alt="" class="card-svg xs" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <h6 class="svg-card-title">Extract data automatically</h6>
                <div class="svg-card-description">AI algorithms can accurately extract key information from paper documents, eliminating the need for manual data entry and reducing errors.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white p-48">
              <div class="card-svg-block">
                <img src="/images/pages/products_zapier-n8n-integration-automation-whyformx-accuracy.svg" loading="lazy" width="128" alt="" class="card-svg xs" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <h6 class="svg-card-title">Validate data</h6>
                <div class="svg-card-description">AI can verify the accuracy and consistency of extracted data, ensuring compliance with industry standards and regulations.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white p-48">
              <div class="card-svg-block">
                <img src="/images/pages/products_zapier-n8n-integration-automation-whyformx-complex.svg" loading="lazy" width="128" alt="" class="card-svg xs" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <h6 class="svg-card-title">Classify documents</h6>
                <div class="svg-card-description">AI can automatically classify documents based on their content, streamlining the sorting and filing process.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-white p-48">
              <div class="card-svg-block">
                <img src="/images/pages/products_zapier-n8n-integration-automation-whyformx-integration.svg" loading="lazy" width="128" alt="" class="card-svg xs" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <h6 class="svg-card-title">Optimize workflows</h6>
                <div class="svg-card-description">AI can identify bottlenecks and inefficiencies in existing workflows, suggesting improvements to enhance productivity.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <FAQSection
    heading="Frequently Asked Questions"
    items={[
      {
        question: "What data does FormX extract from a bill of lading?",
        answer: `FormX extracts shipper and consignee name and address, carrier details, vessel and voyage number, port of loading and discharge, container number, seal number, goods description, quantity, weight, and freight terms. Output is available as JSON, Excel, or CSV. <a href="/schedule-demo">Get in touch</a> to see a demo.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "What bill of lading formats does FormX support?",
        answer: `FormX processes standard paper bills of lading as scanned PDFs or images, as well as digitally generated PDFs from freight management systems. It is template-free and handles varying layouts across shipping lines. <a href="/schedule-demo">Contact us</a> to test your specific format.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "Can FormX integrate with freight and logistics software?",
        answer: `Yes. FormX connects via REST API and has pre-built integrations with Zapier and n8n, enabling direct connection to TMS platforms, ERP systems, and customs management software without custom development. <a href="/schedule-demo">Schedule a demo</a> to discuss your integration.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "Is it safe to upload shipping documents to FormX?",
        answer: `FormX is ISO 27001 and SOC 2 Type II certified. All uploaded documents are encrypted in transit (TLS 1.2+) and at rest (AES-256). Documents are not retained after extraction. Read our <a href="/data-privacy-policy" target="_blank">data privacy policy</a> for more.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "Is there a free trial for bill of lading extraction?",
        answer: `Yes. The web tool is free with no signup required for single document extraction. Batch processing and API access require a free trial account. <a href="https://formextractorai.com/signup" target="_blank">Sign up</a> or <a href="/schedule-demo">contact us</a> to get started.<br />`,
      },
    ]}
  />

  <section class="section whats-new">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-default w-container">
      <div class="whats-new-last-section">
        <div class="whats-new-content-wrap">
          <h2 class="whats-new-last-section-heading color-white">FormX.ai: Your Gateway to a Streamlined Future</h2>
          <div class="color-white">Skip manual eBL data entry with FormX.ai's AI-powered converter. Embrace logistics efficiency today!</div>
        </div>
        <a href="/schedule-demo" class="button-primary button-white w-button">Learn more about FormX.ai's Logistics Solution -&gt;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
